<h2>Checking Accounts</h2>
				<div class="content">
					<p>Members Trust offers two checking account options to meet your financial needs.  Whether you write checks frequently or only occasionally, we have the checking account for you.  Our variety of features and services makes your checking account a smart and flexible financial tool. Click <%= link_to "here", "pdf/membership_application.pdf" %> for an application to set up a new checking account.</p>
