						<li>No minimum balance requirement</li>
						<li>Unlimited check writing</li>
						<li>Overdraft protection from savings account</li>
						<li>Free online banking</li>
						<li>Free online bill payment</li>
						<li>eStatements</li>
						<li>Free debit/check card</li>
						<li>24/7 telephone customer service (800-769-8934)</li>
